title: Bryan-Bryan v Paes-Stepanek US Open 2013 Doubles SF
description:
ATP US Open, 2013.

Doubles, Semi-Final, Bob Bryan/Mike Bryan vs Radek Stepanek/Leander Paes, recording of US Open live stream.

Transcoded from MPEG-2 720p/25 at 8 Mbps by ffmpeg using settings -c:v libx264 -crf 23 -preset veryfast -tune animation -c:a libfdk_aac -ab 64000.

A couple of points were missed, there will be a jump from love to 30 in some game.
